text.header1: Vula amakhonkco ngokuKhuselekileyo kwaye ngokungaziwa usebenzisa i-Kasm Open-in-Isolation.
text.header2: I-Kasm Vula kwi-browser ye-Isolation eyongezelelweyo ibonelela ngokucofa-ekunene kwimenyu yokukhetha ukuvula amakhonkco ewebhu kwi-Workspaces ekwanti isikhangeli. Oku kwenza kube lula kwaye kungenamthungo ukuvula ngokukhuselekileyo ii-URL ezikrokrisayo/ezingakhuselekanga okanye ukugcina ubumfihlo bakho. Kuba iphepha lewebhu linikezelwa ngaphakathi kwesikhangeli sendawo yokusebenza ekude, endaweni yokuba isetyenziswe kwikhompyuter yakho yasekhaya, uyakwazi ukusebenzisana ngokukhuselekileyo nangokungaziwa kwiphepha lewebhu.

title.tooltip1: I-Go izakuvula i-URL kwindawo entsha yokusebenzela, indlela yeSitshixo sokuCasa yeyomsebenzi okhoyo osebenzayo
title.tooltip2: Xa uvula okubhaliweyo kwiseshoni yeeNdawo zokuSebenza zeKasm ngaphandle kokuba umtya uyi-URL esebenzayo iya kudluliselwa kwinjini yokukhangela.
title.tooltip3: Ukuba uvula okubhaliweyo kwiNdawo yokuSebenza ungafuna ukutshintsha uluhlu lwamagama olugqithiselwe kwiNdawo yokuSebenza (Fumana ixhasa iRegExp esemgangathweni enedelimiters /regexp/g)
